---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About aircag, security researcher focused on smart contract auditing, on-chain investigations, and general security research."
>
  <div class="mb-8">
    <h1 class="font-mono text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest">about</h1>
  </div>

  <div
    class="prose prose-invert prose-sm max-w-none
      prose-headings:font-semibold prose-headings:text-slate-100 prose-headings:font-mono
      prose-a:text-[#22d3ee] prose-a:no-underline hover:prose-a:underline
      prose-p:text-slate-300 prose-p:leading-relaxed
      prose-li:text-slate-300
      prose-strong:text-slate-200
      prose-hr:border-[#1e293b]"
  >
    <p>
      I'm aircag, a security researcher focused on smart contract auditing, on-chain investigations,
      and general security research. This blog is where I document findings, writeups, and things I
      find interesting while down the rabbit hole.
    </p>

    <h2>focus areas</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Smart Contract Security</strong></li>
      <li><strong>Blockchain Investigations</strong></li>
      <li><strong>Forensics and Blue Teaming</strong></li>
      <li><strong>General Security Research</strong></li>
    </ul>

    <h2>contact</h2>
    <p>
      <a href="mailto:aircag@proton.me">aircag@proton.me</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
